ank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RED HOT CHILLI PEPPERS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Red_Hot_Chili_Peppers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spectators were heard shrieking when they spotted Cruise standing on the top of the stadium, dressed in a leather jacket and gloves, before seamlessly lowering himself to the ground.\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The moment was also a convenient promotional move for Cruise's forthcomingMission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part Two, which will be released in May 2025, and will mark the eighth time the actor has starred in the franchise since 1992.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3366, \"end\": 3376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Impossible_Foods\", \"score\": 0.9999999998567546, \"rank\": 5.94893075205403e-11, \"text\": \"Impossible\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Impossible_Foods\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Impossible_Foods\"}, {\"begin\": 3379, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dead_reckoning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.991544056377691e-18, \"text\": \"Dead Reckoning\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dead_reckoning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dead_reckoning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after Cruise's stunt, Paramount Pictures, which makes the Mission: Impossible franchise, shared a statement online thanking the actor for his contribution to the industry - before teasing aspects of the forthcoming movie.\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3552, \"end\": 3570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Pictures\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.037542336374003e-18, \"text\": \"Paramount Pictures\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Pictures\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Pictures\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today's closing ceremonies brought our world another incredible moment from Tom Cruise, one that has us looking back on many before it.\", \"from\": 3753, \"to\": 3889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3830, \"end\": 3840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter the mission, he's always accepted it,\\\" said the statement.\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We want to take this opportunity to thank Tom for all that he has done for our industry and art forms as both an actor and a producer,\\\" it continued.\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 4110, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He's consistently strived for the utmost competence across any and all skills that will better the story and experience for the audience.\\\"\", \"from\": 4111, \"to\": 4250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Replying online, Cruise said: \\\"I am incredibly proud of all that we have done together.\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I look forward to sharing our next Mission!\\\"\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4386, \"to\": 4616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4437, \"end\": 4448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5785865651939373e-19, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"